Unlocks the deluxe Advent calendar! You get 25 exclusive fancy premium items.

Only buyable until 31st of December.

Once bought allows you to get all the deluxe items from 1st December until 25th December even after the event ends.

Thank you very much for your support!
And a Merry Christmas to all of you!
